name: The Arc de Triomphe wrapped
description:
This photo was taken in Paris in October 2021 and is composed of 3 superimposed exposures (multiple exposure) of the artwork of Christo and Jeanne-Claude consisting of wrapping the Arc de Triomphe in textile.

This photo is a special edition available in 10 copies.

You can find all my photos at : https://samuelboivin.fr/

Samuel Boivin
